Chief Minister Chamling visits Earthquake damaged area Gangtok 19th September : ( IPR ) To make an assessment of damages caused to houses and properties in the rural and urban areas owing to the 6 . 8 magnitude earthquake which occurred about 6 . 11 pm of 18 / 9 / 2011 the Chief Minister of Sikkim Mr . Pawan Chamling accompanied by the Cabinet Ministers , MLAs , Zilla Adhakshya East , Chief Secretary and Secretaries and HODs , Members of GMC and East District Administration visited the Tashiling Secretariat , offices in and around the Secretariat complex , Sikkim Press and Police Head Quarter today in the morning .